I am that kind of person who would rather give you a story than an introduction. You would be hard put to find something that doesn’t inspire me. Feed me a theme and I will give you back a text, it’s almost as simple as that.

But I’m not just a writer, although writing is a major player in the love triangle of my life. I’m also a musician, a photographer, an explorer, a gamer and a dreamer of far fetched dreams. I'm also a freelance journalist who works as a teacher.

I read. I write. My stories swarm in my head, fly out like bees, birds, butterflies, wasps. Reader beware.
